    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections, while the interior retains that signature new-car scent with supple, untouched leather and pristine carpets. Mechanically, it is flawless, having been meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Every button, switch, and electronic component operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. From the curb-rash-free alloy wheels to the crystal-clear lenses of the headlights, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. It is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to own a piece of automotive perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
