      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one, and it\u2019s been tucked away safely in the garage. It drives like a dream and looks even better. Seriously, you won't find a speck of dust on it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
